Polymorphism means one name and many forms


                        Polymorphism
                   |                   |
            Compile Time            Run Time (Dynamic)
        |               |               |                   |
    Func Overloading





    Funtion Overloading--> Same function name which is performing different tasks 
    there are few conditions for function Overloading
            -> Number of Arguments passed in each function can be different
            -> If the number of Arguments is same, the datatype of atleast 1 Arguments shall be different
            